entry.title: Iridescent Beauty
entry.content:
StarLighttt posted a photo:

People around the world are divided on how the peacock's brilliant feathers can influence luck. In much of the Western world, bringing a peacock feather indoors is bad luck. In the East, particularly India, China and Japan, bringing peacock feathers into the home is a way to increase luck.
